WEBVTT

00:00.097 --> 00:01.291
<i>Previously on "Heartland"...</i>

00:01.398 --> 00:02.956
What is this?

00:03.067 --> 00:04.125
Let's just say now you've got

00:04.234 --> 00:06.327
all the sponsorship
you're gonna need.

00:06.437 --> 00:08.268
I'm gonna miss you, cowboy.

00:09.740 --> 00:11.674
You still haven't told them
about me, have you?

00:11.740 --> 00:12.974
No.

00:13.040 --> 00:14.074
I haven't.

00:14.178 --> 00:15.167
But I will.

00:15.279 --> 00:16.245
Promise?

00:16.379 --> 00:17.870
What's going on, Amy?

00:17.982 --> 00:19.381
What is that supposed to mean?

00:19.717 --> 00:21.241
Man, they are stubborn.

00:22.152 --> 00:23.380
Honey, it's just some tests.

00:23.487 --> 00:26.684
Whatever this is, Mom,
I'm not gonna let you do it alone.

00:26.790 --> 00:28.348
Are you breaking up with me?

00:28.459 --> 00:29.983
Kit!

00:31.495 --> 00:32.723
I can't pretend anymore.

00:32.830 --> 00:34.855
This friends thing
is not working out for me.

